resources.string: By logging into Magpie with your Google account, you are agreeing to our Privacy Policy and our Terms of Use. Magpie 2017.
PLEASE MOVE CLOSER TO COLLECT THIS BADGE
With Magpie, you can find tours, events, walks, scavenger hunts and more around you, known on Magpie as "collections."
Each collection will take you to a series of locations where you will learn fun facts, explore, and earn special badges. Find all the badges to complete your collections!
Win awesome prizes for completing collections. We partner up with some of the best businesses we can find to provide real prizes and exclusive discoutns where you live!
